Package: boosterpak
Title: Declarative Project Package Bundles
Version: 0.5.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Sean", "Thimons", email = "sxthimons@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Sean Thimons [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Sean Thimons <sxthimons@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a TOML manifest for declaring R project package bundles,
    resolving built-in, user, and project packs, and applying them through pak
    and renv.
